										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><b>Launched in October 2022</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">, Decentrawood is an AI-powered Web3 entertainment ecosystem that combines gaming, intelligent AI, the metaverse, social experiences, and digital ownership into a unified platform. With the launch of </span><b>DEOD AI</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">, the ecosystem has expanded to enable users to create, verify, deploy, and use autonomous AI agents for real-world automation and personalized digital experiences. Powered by the </span><b>DEOD</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> token, Decentrawood continues to expand its ecosystem by integrating AI, blockchain technology, and Web3 entertainment into a single decentralized platform. </span></p>
